# Handled Home — Provider Onboarding: Screen Copy + Clause-by-Clause Agreement (California v1)

> **Important**: This is product/legal UX copy for click-to-accept onboarding. It is **not legal advice**. Have California counsel review and tune enforceability (especially anything that resembles non-solicit / non-circumvention).

---

