**Headline:** Good news — demand is growing fast near you.  
**Body:** We’re adding quality providers in **[ZONE]**. If approved, you’ll receive local work routed efficiently with built-in billing and proof-of-work.  
**Bullets:**  
- More paying hours, less dead time  
