# PART D — Opinionated Implementation Notes (to make conversion high + ops sane)

## D1 — Don’t ask for vendor names, SSNs, or complex paperwork in v1
- Collect minimal data, then verify in Ops review.
- Use Stripe flows for tax forms and payouts.

## D2 — Show “Founding Partner spots left” if you can
Scarcity drives conversion, but only if it’s real.

## D3 — Make BYOC feel like “upgrade your customers to premium”
Provide an in-app invite script and a share link:
- “Pay by card + get receipts + bundle services.”

## D4 — Gate “job access” until key steps complete
No provider should receive real jobs until:
- agreement accepted
- payout setup complete
- required compliance docs uploaded (if required)
- approved by ops
